org.apache.juneau.utils

Class MethodExecStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.utils.MethodExecStats
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<MethodExecStats>

    @Bean(bpi="method,runs,running,errors,minTime,maxTime,avgTime,totalTime,exceptions")
public class MethodExecStats
extends Object
implements Comparable<MethodExecStats>
    Basic timing information. Keeps track of number of starts/finishes on tasks and keeps an average run time.
